title: Episode 175: Shawne Merriman
itunes:subtitle: Former NFL star, Shawne Merriman, joins The Fighter and The Kid podcast. The guys discuss the insane dedication it takes to make it in the NFL, the Rio Olympics, Merriman's involvement with the WWE and more.
